description: Welcome to your new sanctuary in the heart of Ebony Park, Midrand! This charming bedroom house is poised to offer you a blend of comfort, convenience, and stylish living. With modern amenities and a welcoming atmosphere, this home is not just a place to live; it’s a place to thrive.
